column5: Probably will be getting one this year but besides that, tomorrow I will be in the kw area (woolwich area) I'd like to do some fishing on the conostogo river for pike, does anyone have a float tube they could lend me for the day around there?
If you're buying one, I'd reccommend the Outcast Float Tubes.  Best I've owned over the years.  http://www.outcastboats.com/outcast/products/default.aspx?id=22
Thanks MB, and just to let everyone know I'm not going to waterloo afterall.
